  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Shaman Spirit Hex</strong><br/><br/><p>The shaman touches a willing creature (including herself) and enshrouds that creature in mist. This grants the creature concealment as the blur spell. The mist dissipates after it causes an attack to miss because of concealment or after 1 minute, whichever comes first. At 8th and 16th levels, the mist lasts for one additional attack. A creature affected by this hex cannot be affected by it again for 24 hours.</p>",
